data.description: Nestled in a tranquil and picturesque neighborhood, this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home awaits you on a spacious .12-acre lot. As you approach, you'll immediately notice the inviting curb appeal, with a well-manicured front lawn and a cozy porch that welcomes you home. The three bedrooms are generously sized, providing comfortable spaces for rest and relaxation. The primary bedroom boasts an en-suite bathroom, offering a private retreat at the end of the day. The additional two bedrooms share a well-appointed bathroom, perfect for family or guests. Sellers are motivated and willing to cover up to $5,000 of buyer's closing costs with a negotiated contract at listing price!
